WorkItem.Description:
I fill the ItemsSource property of the box like this:
---- XAML ----
ItemsSource="{Binding Path=Detail}" ValueMemberBinding="{Binding Title}"
 
---- C# Object Code ----
public class Detail
{
	public int ID { get; set; }
	public string Title { get; set; }
}
 
Now I create a list of two Detail objects whit the same identical title but different IDs and bind it to the AutoCompleteBox.
In this scenario, when I select an item from the combo of the AutoCompleteBox, I always get the same object (the same ID) when I try to read the property "SelectedItem".
